 minor bumps.  The spring plate rests less than 1/4
 inch above the stopper.  As
 I understand the recent adjustment was made to both
 the inner and outer
 splines one position.  Any suggestions on how to
 re-adjust the torsion bar so
 that the spring plate does not knock against the
